console中添加如下方法

function print(){
	var courts="(0,'最高人民法院',null,true),";
	for(var i = 0;i<court_0.length;i++){
		console.log(court_0[i].id+","+court_0[i].sname+",0");
		courts+="("+court_0[i].id+",'"+court_0[i].sname+"',0,"+court_0[i].hasNext+"),";
		if(court_0[i].hasNext){
			var intCourt = eval("court_"+court_0[i].id);
			for(var ii = 0;ii<intCourt.length;ii++){
				console.log(intCourt[ii].id+","+intCourt[ii].sname+","+court_0[i].id);
				courts+="("+intCourt[ii].id+",'"+intCourt[ii].sname+"',"+court_0[i].id+","+intCourt[ii].hasNext+"),";
				if(intCourt[ii].hasNext){
					var subCourt = eval("court_"+intCourt[ii].id);
					for(var iii = 0;iii<subCourt.length;iii++){
						console.log(subCourt[iii].id+","+subCourt[iii].sname+","+intCourt[ii].id);
						courts+="("+subCourt[iii].id+",'"+subCourt[iii].sname+"',"+intCourt[ii].id+","+subCourt[iii].hasNext+"),";
					}
				}
			}	
		}
	}
	console.log(courts);
}
print();
